channel.title: Custom Teleports and Player Commands
channel.description: My home teleport which has a player right of 0 can be used by all players, normal, donor, admin and owner. By custom teleport ::npc1 also has a player right of 0, but can only be used by normal players, and cannot be used by donors, admins, or owner, I have a screenshot down below of my coding, can anyone help me? Also I have only changed coding in commands.java, do I change the coding anywhere else?

item.title: Custom Teleports and Player Commands
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

Your home teleport does not have any rights assigned to it. The c.playerRights segment is what defines the rights, change it to something like c.playerRights >= MINIMUM_RIGHTS_NEEDED.
